<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pl">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>RoyalScent – Perfumy Premium</title>
<style>
body{
    margin:0;
    font-family:Arial, sans-serif;
    background:#f5f5f5;
}
header{
    background:#111;
    color:white;
    padding:20px;
    text-align:center;
    font-size:24px;
}
.hero{
    background:url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1595429035839-c99c298ffdde') center/cover;
    color:white;
    text-align:center;
    padding:100px 20px;
}
.hero h1{
    font-size:40px;
}
.btn{
    background:gold;
    padding:12px 25px;
    text-decoration:none;
    color:black;
    font-weight:bold;
    border-radius:5px;
}
.products{
    padding:40px 20px;
    text-align:center;
}
.grid{
    display:grid;
    grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(250px,1fr));
    gap:20px;
}
.card{
    background:white;
    padding:20px;
    border-radius:10px;
    box-shadow:0 5px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
}
.card img{
    width:100%;
    height:250px;
    object-fit:cover;
}
.price{
    color:green;
    font-size:20px;
    margin:10px 0;
}
button{
    padding:10px 15px;
    background:black;
    color:white;
    border:none;
    cursor:pointer;
    border-radius:5px;
}
footer{
    background:#111;
    color:white;
    text-align:center;
    padding:20px;
    margin-top:40px;
}
</style>
</head>
<body>

<header>
RoyalScent – Perfumy Premium
</header>

<section class="hero">
<h1>Luksusowe zapachy w najlepszej cenie</h1>
<a href="#produkty" class="btn">Zobacz ofertę</a>
</section>

<section class="products" id="produkty">
<h2>Nasze bestsellery</h2>

<div class="grid">

<div class="card">
<img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1592945403244-b3fbafd7f539">
<h3>Arabian Night 100ml</h3>
<p>Intensywny orientalny zapach dla mężczyzn.</p>
<div class="price">129 zł</div>
<button onclick="buy()">Kup teraz</button>
</div>

<div class="card">
<img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1615634260167-c8cdede054de">
<h3>Velvet Rose 100ml</h3>
<p>Zmysłowa kompozycja kwiatowo-ambrowa.</p>
<div class="price">119 zł</div>
<button onclick="buy()">Kup teraz</button>
</div>

<div class="card">
<img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1585386959984-a4155224a1ad">
<h3>Midnight Gold 100ml</h3>
<p>Elegancki zapach unisex o dużej trwałości.</p>
<div class="price">139 zł</div>
<button onclick="buy()">Kup teraz</button>
</div>

</div>
</section>

<footer>
© 2026 RoyalScent | Darmowa dostawa od 199 zł
</footer>

<script>
function buy(){
    window.location.href="https://allegro.pl/";
}
</script>

</body>
</html>
